data.description: Affordable Roosevelt Home for Sale - 2 Bedrooms, 3 Bathrooms, 2 Zone Oil Heat, Finished Basement, and More! Welcome to your new home in  Roosevelt. This property offers comfortable one floor living complete with desirable features on a quiet, traffic-free street, providing a serene and safe environment for your family. Stay warm and cozy during the colder months with the energy-efficient two-zone oil heating system. The full finished basement is a versatile space that can be used for various purposes, such as a recreation area, home office, or an extra living space. The basement also features a convenient laundry area, making chores a breeze, and includes a full Bath. Additional storage space is available in the full attic, perfect for stowing away seasonal items and keepsakes. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a charming home in Roosevelt.
